- ER10 release

* Thu Jun 23 2016 Adam Mercer <adam.mercer@ligo.org> 1.2.8-1
- ER9 release

* Fri Mar 25 2016 Adam Mercer <adam.mercer@ligo.org> 1.2.7-1
- Pre O2 packaging test release
